Otyebis Crew:




The Decepticon leader's transmission was received, and the receiver was a 
little confused.

"Errr...Megatron was it?  Do you mean you would like an audience with the 
head of the IGL, President Kaiser?  If so come to coordinates (yadda, yadda), 
it will bring you within the perimeter guard of the Otyebis and near an 
entryway of the base where you will be escorted inside.  We suggest bringing 
an escort of only two at the maximum."
